[[File:Soldier (Burthorpe) chathead.png|left]]
'''Soldiers''' are members of the [[Burthorpe]] [[Imperial Guard]]. There are some Soldiers that you cannot attack who are doing military drills in the main area of Burthorpe. They appear to be wearing [[spiny helmet]]s coloured black without the spikes. When talking to them they will say a random sentence in Latin. They are trained by [[Sergeant]]s.

